data.description: Large beautifully designed all brick home, located on a quiet cozy street in the highly coveted master plan community of Fall Creek.  This stunning David Weekley Medford 1 story plan features 3-bedrooms, 3 baths and a game room. The Formal entryway has 12 ft ceilings and is flanked by your Formal Dining on the right and a spacious home office on the left. The large open concept living room boasts stylish white built-in cabinets with glass shelving and columns as you enter. The spacious kitchen has lots of cabinet & counter space, a center island cooktop that has gas piping if you choose to convert, a breakfast bar, breakfast room, butler's pantry and walk-in food pantry. The Large Primary Suite has a sitting area, dual vanities in the bath, separate shower, and an extra-large walk-in closet. Secondary bedrooms share a Jack & Jill bath with double sinks. In the community, stay in shape on the convenient jogging trail that surrounds the green space! This beauty is definitely a must see!
